@startuml

participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant PostgreSQL
participant "Python FastAPI" as FastAPI
participant Ollama

Frontend -> Backend: POST /v1/ia (descricao, boardId, columnId)
Backend -> PostgreSQL: INSERT Job
PostgreSQL --> Backend: Job salvo (jobId)

Backend -> FastAPI: POST /api/v1/generate-backlog (jobId, descricao)
note over Backend, FastAPI: Retry até 5x se conexão falhar

Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK (AcceptedResponse)

FastAPI -> Ollama: Llama infer
Ollama --> FastAPI: JSON issues

note over FastAPI: Valida JSON\nRetry se JSON inválido

FastAPI -> Backend: POST /v1/ia/callback
Backend -> PostgreSQL: createBulkIssues no board Kanban
PostgreSQL --> Backend: 200 OK

note over Frontend: Usuário recarrega o board\npara ver as novas issues

@enduml